  export (root element, attribute names/shapes, nesting) but trimmed of
  fields the leveling-plan parser does not read (Items, Calcs internals,
  full passive tree node lists, etc). Gem nameSpecs use the exact vendored
  gem names from vendor/exile-leveling/data/gems.json, including the
  " Support" suffix that support gems carry in-game, so enrichment
  (required_level / is_support) actually resolves.
-->
